{
  "stem": "7683.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were so organized and [? of ?] [? these ?] days, they supposed to come for a fitting or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were already people there assigned, when they come, to kill them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so there was going on, the whole day was it going on, and there were killed a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew all the time, because there were people which were-- their work was to move from place to place, and they always told us how far the uprising progressed.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we knew there, already so many got killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was tension, surely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was tension-- afraid that it doesn't come out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You kept quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You didn't talk about, and you did always like nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then where I worked, it was the warehouses from clothes, so the Germans would supervise us, or they chaperoned us, or whatever you call it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were called with a pretense to the magazine, and they got killed there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But still the work went through like nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There-- there was a-- there was in an office was a German what was the plan that he has to be killed, because it was a very important position.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was in a place where everything had to go through there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So if he would have caught something happened, that would be the end of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were two people assigned to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At once, one of them got afraid and didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I figured we have 10-- in that time, around 10 were already killed of the Germans, and if we stopped now, [? then ?] for sure dead.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I'm not a big hero, I guess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I think my brains dictated me, just go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Do it.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
